Package: strutR
Type: Package
Title: Struthers Wetting-Front Model for Infiltration, Redistribution, and Drainage
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      given = "Tommaso", family = "Martini",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "tommaso.martini@unito.it",
      comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000")
    )
Description: Reference implementation in R of the Struthers multiple-wetting-front
    gravitational infiltration and redistribution model for soil-water balance
    applications (Struthers, Hinz, and Sivapalan, 2006, Water Resources Research,
    42(6), W06406, <doi:10.1029/2005WR004645>). The model simulates one-dimensional
    unsaturated flow as a sequence of wetting fronts under rainfall and drydown
    conditions, including front merging, redistribution, and drainage. Includes
    functions for forward simulation, parameterization, and visualization.
